riendly support team anytime. We’re here to assist you around the clock.\",\"checkDetails\":\"Check Details\",\"chooseCryptoOrFiat\":\"Choose crypto or fiat when you pay\",\"claimNow\":\"Claim Now\",\"claimRewards\":\"Claim Rewards\",\"coinEstAprRate\":\"{coin} {apr_rate} est APR\",\"competitiveTradingRates\":\"Competitive trading rates\",\"completeVerifUnlock\":\"Complete verification to unlock higher limits, more features, and uninterrupted trading.\",\"complianceTrust\":\"Compliance \u0026 trust\",\"contactSupportWithLink\":\"If you have any questions, please contact Customer Support through Live Chat or submit a request via \u003ca href=\\\"https://www.bybit.tr/en-TR/help-center/s/webform\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\"\u003ethis form\u003c/a\u003e.\",\"contactUs\":\"Contact us\",\"continueWithOptions\":\"Continue with one of the following:\",\"copyrightMoneyPartners\":\"Copyright © MONEY PARTNERS CO., LTD All rights\",\"countriesAndRegions\":\"Countries and regions\",\"createAccountEmail\":\"Create an account with your email, Google or Apple.\",\"createAccountMinutes\":\"Create your account in minutes\",\"cryptoCFDsRiskInfo\":\"Cryptocurrency CFDs may incur losses due to price fluctuations. As leveraged trading allows investments that exceed the margin amount, losses may exceed your initial margin. If the maintenance margin ratio falls below the required level, your positions may be forcibly liquidated. During periods of sudden market volatility, losses may also exceed the margin amount.\",\"cryptoExchangeBiz\":\"Cryptocurrency Exchange Business\",\"cryptoKnowledgeHub\":\"Crypto knowledge hub\",\"cryptoLegalTender\":\"Cryptocurrencies are not legal tender (domestic or foreign currency), and their value is not guaranteed by any entity. They may only be used for payment with the consent of the recipient and generally do not have compulsory circulation.\\n\\nTrading cryptocurrencies or exchanging them for other assets may result in losses due to price fluctuations. Prices offered by Money Partners may differ from broader market rates, and low liquidity may prevent transactions from being executed at intended prices. Cryptocurrency prices may also fluctuate due to changes in supply and demand, inflation, currency movements, or broader market trends.\\n\\nTransactions may be delayed or interrupted due to system failures or communication issues. If you lose your private key, you may be unable to access your held cryptocurrencies, potentially resulting in a total loss of value. While we manage customer assets separately, this does not guarantee the return of assets in the event of bankruptcy.\",\"cryptoTradingForBeginners\":\"Crypto trading for beginners\",\"cryptoUpdatesTip\":\"Stay at the heart of crypto — access news, updates and offers from Bybit Georgia. You can unsubscribe at any time in accordance with our Privacy Policy.\",\"CSP_announcement\":\"Announcement\",\"CSP_announcement_cancel_orders\":\"We recommend canceling any pending orders before the system shutdown. Orders that remain open at the time of shutdown will be automatically canceled by Bybit TR. You may place new orders once the maintenance is complete.\",\"CSP_announcement_customer_support\":\"If you have any questions, please contact Customer Support through Live Chat or submit a request via {link}.\",\"CSP_announcement_maintenance_schedule\":\"Bybit TR will conduct scheduled system maintenance from April 4, 2026, 12AM (Turkish time) to April 5, 2026, 11:59PM (Turkish time). The maintenance is expected to last approximately 48 hours.\",\"CSP_announcement_market_risks\":\"Please note that crypto markets remain active while our platform is offline, and asset prices may fluctuate. The maintenance period may extend beyond the estimated timeframe provided above. We strongly recommend managing your positions and taking any necessary actions before April 4, 2026, 12AM (Turkish time).\\nBybit TR cannot be held responsible for market-driven price fluctuations or any resulting outcomes during this period.\",\"CSP_announcement_securitySystemInt\":\"For security and system integrity, all users will be automatically signed out during the maintenance period. You will need to log in again once the maintenance is completed and services resume.\",\"CSP_announcement_services_api\":\"All API functionalities\",\"CSP_announcement_services_deposits\":\"Deposits, withdrawals and internal transfers\",\"CSP_announcement_services_login\":\"Account login and new account registration\",\"CSP_announcement_services_suspended\":\"During this period, all Bybit TR services will be temporarily suspended, including but not limited to:\",\"CSP_announcement_services_transactions\":\"All trading activities\",\"customerSupport247\":\"24/7 customer support across 240+ countries and regions.\",\"deepLiquidityAcrossMarkets\":\"Deep liquidity across markets\",\"deposit1\":\"Deposit\",\"depositCrypto\":\"Deposit Crypto\",\"depositEur\":\"Deposit EUR easily\",\"depositNow1\":\"Deposit Now\",\"disagree\":\"Disagree\",\"dontJustHodlGrowCrypto\":\"Don't just HODL. Grow your crypto holdings the smart way.\",\"downloadApp1\":\"Download App\",\"downloadNow\":\"Download Now\",\"doYouAgreeToReceiveMkt\":\"Do you agree to receive marketing materials from Bybit Georgia?\",\"earnKycRewardsByVerifyingIdentity\":\"Earn {kyc_rewards_number} by verifying your identity\",\"earnUpToAprOnUsdt\":\"Earn up to {apr_number} APR on USDT\",\"emailOrMobileNumber\":\"Email or mobile number\",\"emailPhone\":\"Email/Phone\",\"enterAddressAndCode\":\"Enter your address and the code sent here.\",\"euCompliesWithReg\":\"Bybit EU complies with EU regulations under MiCAR\",\"euOperatesFromAT\":\"Bybit EU operates from Austria through a local legal entity.\",\"euRegulatoryStandards\":\"Every purchase follows EU regulatory standards.\",\"eventOrganizedByBy\":\"This event is organized by Bybit Fintech FZE, a limited liability company registered in Dubai, United Arab Emirates, located at The Offices 4 – On